title: ‘Survivor,’ Season 42, Episode 3 With Ethan Zohn
description:
Tyson and Riley are joined by ‘Survivor: Africa’ winner Ethan Zohn to break down the third episode of Season 42. They discuss Maryanne finding another advantage, Jonathan’s epic challenge performance, and Daniel’s slew of blunders. Plus, Tyson shares a story about drawing rocks and they hand out this week’s superlatives.
Hosts: Tyson Apostol and Riley McAtee
Guest: Ethan Zohn
Associate Producer: Mike Wargon
